cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.DS, cs.FL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper discusses model checking approaches for temporal logic formulas. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper mentions executing the model checking procedure "on-the-fly" for a process language. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper proposes an efficient model checking procedure for certain classes of systems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the efficiency of the proposed procedure compared to a global PCTL model checker. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with temporal logic formulas and their interpretation in a language.
